channel.title: SRL error (color?)
channel.description:
Good evening, my 1st post is in here indicating i'mnew to this ;) I tried following the SRL setup guide, but encountered this message when trying to enter the setup code at the bottom of your post:
Line 871: [Error] (6737:11): Unknown identifier 'FindColorCircleD' in script C:\Program Files\SCAR 2.03\includes\srl\srl\core\Color.scar Failed when compiling
any help? :) thanks guys

item.title: SRL error (color?)
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Move all the SRL plugins to the \Program Files\SCAR 2.03\plugins\ folder, close and open SCAR again then try again.
